கீழ்நிலையில் இருந்தாலும் இழிகுணம் இல்லாதவர் கீழ்மக்கள் அல்லர்.
</br>
</br>
Even if they are noble, those that are not noble are not 
noble: and even if they are low-born, those that are not 
low are not low.
%
